# ── Subject line ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#   │         │        │
#   │         │        └─ ≤80 chars, imperative, no period
#   │         └────────── Optional scope (e.g. ui, providers, build)
#   └──────────────────── Type: feat | fix | docs | refactor | chore | test
#
# Examples:
#   feat(providers): add OpenAI provider
#   fix(ui): correct Shadow DOM event retargeting
#   docs: update README with architecture overview
#
# ── Body — describe what and why (not how) ───────────────────────
#
# A blank line separates subject from body. Explain the motivation,
# context, and reasoning. Wrap at 72 characters.
#
#
# ── Footer (optional) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
# Closes #<issue>
